Disciplinary Counsel
v.
Doumbas 2016-1149 Supreme Court of Ohio. June 27, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell and Fischer, JJ., dissent.

RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

On motion for reconsideration. Motion granted in part and April 19, 2018 entry vacated. The respondent may file a new petition for reinstatement on or after February 21, 2019.
